review: I visited Taqueria El Rapido expecting a great taco experience based on the reviews, but I was a bit underwhelmed. The tacos were decent, but the meat was a little dry, and the overall flavor didn't quite meet my expectations. The salsa bar was a nice touch, but it didn't make up for the lackluster main dish. I might give it another try, but for now, it's just an average experience.
